.SH DESCRIPTION
.I MrEd
is the PLT's graphical Scheme
implementation.
It embeds and extends 
.I MzScheme
with a graphical user interface (GUI) toolbox.
.PP
.I DrScheme
is the graphical development environment for creating
.I MzScheme
and
.I MrEd
applications.

.SH X OPTIONS

